## Transformers

Transformers adapt requests/responses for different API formats.

### Available Built-in Transformers

- `Anthropic` - Preserves original Claude format
- `deepseek` - DeepSeek API format
- `gemini` - Google Gemini API format
- `openrouter` - OpenRouter API format (with provider routing)
- `groq` - Groq API format
- `maxtoken` - Set specific max_tokens limit
- `tooluse` - Optimize tool usage via tool_choice
- `reasoning` - Process reasoning_content field
- `sampling` - Handle temperature, top_p, etc.
- `enhancetool` - Error tolerance for tool calls
- `cleancache` - Remove cache_control fields
- `vertex-gemini` - Vertex AI authentication

### Global Transformer (All Models)
```json
{
  "name": "openrouter",
  "transformer": {
    "use": ["openrouter"]
  }
}
```

### Model-Specific Transformer
```json
{
  "name": "deepseek",
  "transformer": {
    "use": ["deepseek"],
    "deepseek-chat": {
      "use": ["tooluse"]
    }
  }
}
```

### Transformer with Options
```json
{
  "name": "custom-provider",
  "transformer": {
    "use": [
      ["maxtoken", { "max_tokens": 16384 }]
    ]
  }
}
```

### Custom Transformers

Create your own transformer:

```json
{
  "transformers": [
    {
      "path": "/path/to/custom-transformer.js",
      "options": {
        "project": "my-project"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

