## Running Claude Code Router

### Start the Router
```bash
ccr code
```

This will:
1. Start the router proxy server on `http://localhost:3456`
2. Launch Claude Code configured to use the router
3. Route all requests according to your configuration

### Restart After Config Changes
```bash
ccr restart
```

### Stop the Router
```bash
ccr stop
```

### Check Router Status
```bash
ccr status
```

